1. *Odgovorio* sam na tvoj mejl (I replied to your email).
2. On *odgovara* na pitanja (He answers the questions).
3. Nije mi *odgovorio* na poruku (He didn't answer my message).
4. On je *odgovoran* za tu grešku (He is responsible for that mistake).
5. *Odgovori* mi brzo, molim te! (Answer me quickly, please!)
6. Oni su *odgovorili* na sve naše zahteve (They responded to all our requests).
7. Ti si mi *odgovorila* na pitanje (You answered my question).
8. Načelnik će *odgovarati* za svoje postupke (The chief will be held accountable for his actions).
9. Nemojte *odgovarati* na ovaj mejl, to je samo obaveštenje (Don't reply to this email, it's just an announcement).
10. Sutra ćeš morati *da odgovoriš* na testu (Tomorrow you will have to answer on the test).